articles.author: Margaret Brennan
articles.title: Iran prisoner swap: 5 Americans back in U.S. after being released in complex diplomatic deal - CBS News
articles.description: The prisoner swap included the transfer of $6 billion in unfrozen Iranian oil assets and the release of five Iranians facing charges in the U.S.
